queries.name: Claim -  claimsList
Claim - PolicyList
Claim - suspicious
queries.query:
USE main.fsi_smart_claims;
select
  count(suspicious_activity) as fraud
FROM
  claim_insights
where
  suspicious_activity = true
  and to_date(claim_date) >= '{{start_date}}'
  and to_date(claim_date) <= '{{end_date}}';

queries.name: Claim - Insight
queries.query:
USE main.fsi_smart_claims;
select
  CASE
    WHEN valid_date = 'NOT VALID' THEN 1
    ELSE 0
  END as valid_policy,
  CASE
    WHEN reported_severity_check = 'Severity matches the report' THEN 1
    ELSE 0
  END as correct_severity_assessment,
  CASE
    WHEN valid_amount = 'claim value more than premium' THEN 1
    ELSE 0
  END as approve_claim_amount,
  claim_amount_total,
  claim_amount_injury,
  claim_amount_property,
  claim_amount_vehicle,
  incident_severity as reported_severity,
  -- severity as predicted_severity,
  reported_severity_check,
  valid_amount,
  valid_date
from
  claim_insights
where
  claim_no = '{{claim_number}}';

queries.name: Claim - getPolicy
queries.query:
USE main.fsi_smart_claims;
select
  *
from
  claim_insights
where
  POLICY_NO = "{{policy_number}}";

queries.name: Claim -  telematic_insights

query_draft.draft_text:
USE main.fsi_smart_claims;
select
  CHASSIS_NO,
  avg(high_speed) as speeding,
  CASE
    WHEN avg(high_speed) < 0.25 THEN 0
    ELSE 1
  END as speeding_more_than_25percent
from
  (
    select
      chassis_no,
      claim_no,
      claim_date,
      policy_no,
      CASE
        WHEN speed_check = 'High Speed' THEN 1
        WHEN speed_check = 'Normal Speed' THEN 0
        ELSE -1000
      END as high_speed,
      claim_amount_total,
      incident_severity as reported_severity
    from
      claim_insights
  ) a
where
  a.claim_no = "{{claim_number}}"
group by
  CHASSIS_NO,
  claim_no;
query_draft.original_query_text:
USE dbdemos.fsi_smart_claims;
select
  CHASSIS_NO,
  avg(high_speed) as speeding,
  CASE
    WHEN avg(high_speed) < 0.25 THEN 0
    ELSE 1
  END as speeding_more_than_25percent
from
  (
    select
      chassis_no,
      claim_no,
      claim_date,
      policy_no,
      CASE
        WHEN speed_check = 'High Speed' THEN 1
        WHEN speed_check = 'Normal Speed' THEN 0
        ELSE -1000
      END as high_speed,
      claim_amount_total,
      incident_severity as reported_severity
    from
      claim_insights
  ) a
where
  a.claim_no = "{{claim_number}}"
group by
  CHASSIS_NO,
  claim_no;

queries.name: Claim - getClaim
queries.query:
USE main.fsi_smart_claims;;
select
  claim_no,
  claim_amount_total,
  claim_amount_injury,
  claim_amount_property,
  claim_amount_vehicle,
  to_date(claim_date),
  incident_type,
  incident_severity,
  incident_date,
  collision_type,
  collision_number_of_vehicles_involved,
  driver_age,
  driver_insured_relationship,
  driver_license_issue_date,
  months_as_customer,
  number_of_witnesses,
  suspicious_activity
from
  claim_insights
where
  claim_no = '{{claim_number}}';

  and to_date(claim_date) <= '{{end_date}}';
